  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  faqs={faqs}
  article={{
    headline: "Buyer Screening Tools: How Breeders Vet Applicants, Verify Program Fit, and Decide Who to Place With",
    description: "Buyer screening tools help breeders collect, organize, and evaluate applicant information before placing an animal. The four criteria, phased process, and questions that reveal real fit.",
